2. John Legend - He has been doing regular Duet Sessions live streams on Instagram.

3. Miley Cyrus - She has been hosting weekly Bright Minded live streams on Instagram.

4. BTS - The South Korean group has been doing weekly live stream concerts called Bang Bang Con.

5. Elton John - He has been hosting Living Room Concert for America on Fox, featuring performances from various artists.

6. Eric Clapton - He has been streaming live concerts on his YouTube channel.

7. Billie Eilish - She has done a few live stream performances, including one for NPR's Tiny Desk Concerts.

These are just a few examples - there are many other artists doing live streams as well, so keep an eye out and see who suits your taste!
